  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "25. Un Benjamina Behrmi\nfapulzejahs Abneram pakkat/ un\ntappe par Pulku / un stahweja\nweena Pakalna Wirs-Galla.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "26. Tad fauze Abnersus Jo-\nabu / un fazztia : Woj tad tas\nSobbins muhsham rihs? ne sin-\nni tu/ ka tas pehdtagi gann ruhē-\nti buhs? un zikilgi tu teem Can-\ndim ne fazzisti/ ka teem huhs at-\ngreestees no Pakkatdsihshchanas\npehz taweem Brahteemi?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "27. Tad fazztia Joabs: Tik\nteescham ka Deews dsihwo/kaut\ntu buhtu schoriht ta runnajs/ tee\nLaudis jaw buhtu nowehrsti/ ik-\nweens no fawa Brahta Pakkat-\ndsihshchanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "28. Tad puhte Joabs ar to\nBasuni/ un wiſſi Laudis pastah-\nweja/ un ne dsinne wairē Israē-\nkam pakkat / un mittejahs kau-\ntees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "29. Tad gabje Abners un twi-\nna Wihri zaurn Nakti pahr to\nKlaijumu/ un gabje pahr to Jar-\ndanu/ un pahrstaigaja wiſſu Bi-\ntronu/ un nahze uhs Mainaim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "30. Un Joabs atgreeſehs no\nAbnera/ un fapulzinaja wiſſus\nLaudis. Tad truhke no Dahwida\nKalpeem dewinpadesmits Wihri/\nun Asaēls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "31. Bet Dahwida Kalpt bij\nno Benjamina un Abnera Wih-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "32. Un tee pazehle Asaēlu/ un\naprakke to fawa Tehwa Kappa/\nkas Betlemē bija. Un Joabs gah-\nje ar fatweem Wihreem zauru\nNakti / ka Gaisina teem tapp\nEebronā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta III. Nodalla.\nDahwida Dehli/ kas Eebronā dsimmuschti:\n2. Abners friht no fawa Kunga Jsboſeta pe-\nDahwida : 6. Atnefs Dahwidam fawu Gee-\nwu Mikali : 16. Pamahza Israēlu / ka tee-\nDahwidu par Kehnizu darritu : 17. Tohp ao-\nJoaba gaur Wiltu nodurts: 22. Pahr ke-\nDahwids gauschi scheblojahs : 28/31. Un ata-\nsihst tee Laudis/ ka Dahwids nenoseedsigs ir-\npee Abnera Nahweg : 37.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "1. Nilgam tappē farrohts\nW starp Saula Nammu /\nun starp Dahwida\nNammu. Bet Dahwids gabje\nun stiprinajahs/ un tee no Saula\nNamma gabje un tappē wahjaki.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "2. Un Dahwidam dsimme\nDehti Eebronā/wirna pirmdsim-\nmts bija Ammons / no Afinoa-\nmas tahs Jesreeeliterenes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "3. Un wirna ohtrs bija Kile-\nabs no Abigailes/ Nahbala See-\nwas ta Karmelitera : Un tastre-\nſchajs/ Absoloms / tas Dehts no\nMāākas / Talinaja ta Kehniza\nno Gesura Meitas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "4. Un tas zettortajs Adoni-\nlas Dehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "5. Un tas festajs Jetreams no\nEglas Dahwida Seevas. Sche-\ndsimme Dahwidam Eebronā.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
